text: I Will is the fifth Korean language studio album by the South Korean pop-rock band F.T. Island, released by FNC Entertainment on 23 March 2015. The music video for the title song Pray was released on the same date, produced by ZanyBros. The band pre-released the Korean version of their Japanese song "To the Light" from the album. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:F.T.
